🧠 BrainScan – AI Medical Diagnostic Platform


🚀 Overview

BrainScan is a Full-Stack AI-powered healthcare platform that analyzes brain MRI scans using Deep Learning (CNN) to assist in early detection of neurological diseases.

The platform provides:

AI-based MRI diagnosis
Automated medical report generation
Doctor–patient communication system
Secure hybrid data architecture
⚙️ Tech Stack
Frontend
React.js
SCSS
Framer Motion
Lucide Icons
Backend
FastAPI (Python)
REST API
AI inference (CNN model integration)
Databases
MySQL (structured data: users, appointments)
MongoDB (MRI scans, reports, chat data)
DevOps
Docker
Docker Compose
Microservices architecture
🧠 AI System
Convolutional Neural Network (CNN)
MRI brain scan classification
Abnormality detection
Automatic medical report generation (PDF)
Real-time inference via FastAPI
🏗️ System Architecture
Frontend (React)
      ↓
Backend (FastAPI)
      ↓
 ┌──────────────┬──────────────┬──────────────┐
 │              │              │              │
MySQL        MongoDB         AI Model (CNN)
Users/RDV    MRI/Reports     Diagnosis Engine
✨ Features
👨‍⚕️ Doctor Panel
Upload MRI scans
AI diagnosis results
Generate medical reports
Manage appointments
🧑 Patient Panel
View medical reports
Book appointments
Track diagnosis history
🛠️ Admin Panel
Manage doctors & patients
Approve doctor registrations
Control specialties
💬 Communication System
Real-time chat (Doctor ↔ Patient)
Post-diagnosis follow-up
AI medical chatbot assistant
🔐 Security
Role-based access control (Admin / Doctor / Patient)
Doctor pre-registration code system
Secure medical data storage
🐳 Run with Docker
1. Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/FahemAoudia/BrainScan-AI-Medical-Diagnostic-Platform.git
cd BrainScan-AI-Medical-Diagnostic-Platform
2. Start project
docker-compose up --build
📦 Services
Backend
Port: 5000
Depends on MySQL + MongoDB
Frontend
Port: 3000
MySQL
Database: brainscandb
MongoDB
Stores MRI scans & reports
🧠 Project Vision

BrainScan aims to bring AI into healthcare by improving MRI analysis accuracy and reducing diagnostic time through automation and intelligent systems.

